data.description: NO BACK NEIGHBORS!!!  The grand entry pulls you in to an open concept floor plan. Family gatherings are a joy in this open concept kitchen.  The maple cabinets and granite countertops feel like luxury.  There is plenty of room in this open concept home to entertain or just relax and enjoy the serenity of being home. The wrought iron spindles are another touch of luxury as the lead you upstairs to the second floor family room! The custom backyard deck with covered patio and custom privacy wall are perfect for entertaining or just relaxing in the backyard oasis. Pride of ownerships is evident when you walk through the door.  Look no further, this home is yours!!!  Book your showing today and lets start a conversation about making this home yours.
